value.0: Forestwalkers for years, rangers that is, have policed the forest for those who threaten to destroy the lands habitats, surroundings, and vegitations, they are said to possess great skills at hiding in the forest.  These chains, though they bare no mark of a maker, are clearly magical in nature to anyone who views them.
Though obviously magical in nature, the dress bares no marks of it's original creator.
The greatest work of the elves are their elven armor, some of the most prized armor in all of Neverwinter.  Whether drow or sylvan design all elven works are a masterpiece unlike any other.
This simple vest is plain but well-constructed of good quality silk in dusky colors. The fabric feels slightly slippery to the touch.
